#

Beef Empanadas with Chimichurri Sauce

$30
500 kcal

Allergens:

GlutenEgg

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinComfort Food

Tags:

BeefPastryArgentinian CuisineComfort Food

Description

Savory ground beef wrapped in flaky pastry, served with a zesty chimichurri sauce.

Ingredients

  • Ground Beef: 6 lb
  • Onion: 2, diced
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Bell Peppers: 2, diced
  • Cumin: 2 tsp
  • Paprika: 2 tsp
  • Oregano: 1 tsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Empanada Dough: 12 sheets
  • Egg: 1, beaten for egg wash
  • Fresh Parsley: 1 cup, chopped
  • Red Wine Vinegar: 1/4 cup
  • Olive Oil (for chimichurri): 1/2 cup
  • Garlic (for chimichurri): 2 cloves, minced
  • Red Pepper Flakes: 1/2 tsp
